AIM_MAP_HLO_RM_V2
------------------
Some of you may know the original map from cs1.6, named aim_map_hlo. I like this map so mutch that i remaked it twice now! Here's the 2nd remake!

For the first remake follow this link : [Remake no.1](http://www.gamebanana.com/maps/147404)

- **I recommend this second remake for Deathmatch-Mode!**

- Every weapon has now additional magazin included, so you have only 30 shots. This is an AIM - map! Aim, than fire! Save your bullets and survive the round to get a full magazin! 

Hf playing

DA!M
